# Static cURL 8.18.0 with HTTP3

## Components

- libcurl/8.18.0
- OpenSSL/3.6.0
- zlib/1.3.1
- brotli/1.2.0
- zstd/1.5.7
- c-ares/1.34.6
- libidn2/2.3.8
- libpsl/0.21.5
- libssh2/1.11.1
- nghttp2/1.68.0
- nghttp3/1.14.0

## Protocols

dict file ftp ftps gopher gophers http https imap imaps ipfs ipns mqtt pop3 pop3s rtsp scp sftp smb smbs smtp smtps telnet tftp ws wss

## Features

alt-svc asyn-rr AsynchDNS brotli HSTS HTTP2 HTTP3 HTTPS-proxy HTTPSRR IDN IPv6 Largefile libz NTLM PSL SSL SSLS-EXPORT threadsafe TLS-SRP TrackMemory UnixSockets zstd

## License

This binary includes various open-source software such as curl, openssl, zlib, brotli, zstd, libidn2, libssh2, nghttp2, ngtcp2, nghttp3. Their license information has been compiled and is included in the dev package.
